title: Carolina gives validity to 5-0 start winning in Seattle
text:
> North Carolina Carolina gives validity to 5-0 start winning in Seattle Carolina Panthers tight end Ed Dickson, left, flies toward Seattle Seahawks strong safety Kam Chancellor (31) after Chancellor intercepted a pass in the second half of an NFL football game, Sunday, Oct. 18, 2015, in Seattle. (AP Photo/Stephen Brashear)
